<para id="fs-idm119939248">Center for Disease Control and Prevention. &#8220;Teen Drivers: Fact Sheet,&#8221; Injury Prevention &amp; Control: Motor Vehicle Safety,  October 2, 2012. Available online at http://www.cdc.gov/Motorvehiclesafety/Teen_Drivers/teendrivers_factsheet.html (accessed May 15, 2013).</para>
